  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Are aged 3 years or older

          -  Have achromatopsia confirmed by a retinal specialist (CI or PI)

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Are females who are pregnant or breastfeeding

          -  Have participated in another research study involving an investigational medicinal
             therapy for ocular disease within the last 6 months

          -  Have any other condition that the CI/PI considers makes them inappropriate for entry
             into the trial
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
